nodes.text: Tanne Kinalos was the partner of Kinalos, a New Republic soldier. They lived together on Coruscant around the time of the Galactic Civil War. Together they had at least two sons and a daughter, Henia.

During the Imperial Civil War that followed in the aftermath of the Second Battle of Coruscant in 10 ABY, the Kinalos home was occupied by Imperial Stormtroopers. Tanne and the rest of the family were forced to flee, leaving many of their possessions behind. Serving with the New Republic Army, Kinalos later returned to his ruined home, clearing Imperial forces from it before abandoning it for good.
